; Bench fixture -- NOT game content. dummy_baseline.tres with ONLY `regen_per_sec` changed to 8.0
; (the sea star's authored value), so the measured ratio attributes to the regeneration race alone.
;
; MORTAL MODE ONLY: immortal mode floods current_health past max_health, which gates the heal off
; entirely -- an immortal regen column silently measures baseline. The probe also has to drive
; tick_regen by hand (it turns enemy physics off to hold the field still).

